text: Clara Kichenama-Gourouvaya (born 10 May 1999) is a Martiniquais footballer who plays as a defender for the Martinique women's national team. ==International career== Kichenama-Gourouvaya capped for Martinique at senior level during the 2014 CONCACAF Women's Championship. On the club level, she plays for Emulation in Martinique. ==References== ==External links== Category:Living people Category:Martiniquais women's footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Martinique women's international footballers Category:1999 births
